1
00:00:07,260 --> 00:00:10,700
Have you ever heard about that

2
00:00:10,700 --> 00:00:13,580
the cliff of a snow mountain

3
00:00:14,100 --> 00:00:19,220
once fascinated numerous people?

4
00:00:20,900 --> 00:00:24,140
Legend has it that,

5
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,940
there were treasures at the peak

6
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:32,860
but also there was a bottomless chasm hidden over there.

7
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:37,900
The smart, the fool

8
00:00:37,940 --> 00:00:40,740
and the kind people,

9
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:47,220
all are familiar to you.

10
00:00:48,100 --> 00:00:51,660
On the mountainside, on the cliff,

11
00:00:51,980 --> 00:00:54,580
on the cloud,

12
00:00:54,980 --> 00:01:00,100
and in the human world,

13
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:19,220
snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly.

14
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,980
Joy of Life Season 1

15
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,900
Episode 36

16
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,080
Are you really the Saintess?

17
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,120
Doesn't the Saintess wipe her hands?

18
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,630
What a temper!

19
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:55,510
Tell me.

20
00:01:56,270 --> 00:01:57,000
How on earth

21
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,270
can you help me kill Xiao En?

22
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,000
I really can't help you do that.

23
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,830
The mission and the cavalry are both around.

24
00:02:02,270 --> 00:02:03,680
If I let you kill Xiao En,

25
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,440
I'm sure to lose my job.

26
00:02:05,630 --> 00:02:06,950
You can come to Beiqi instead.

27
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,240
It's too cold. I'm not used to the weather.

28
00:02:10,550 --> 00:02:12,080
I can assassinate him at the worst.

29
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:13,520
I'll guard him myself.

30
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,030
Plus the cavalry,

31
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:16,800
feel free to have a try.

32
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,190
I can hold you hostage.

33
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:23,000
I'm just a little envoy.

34
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,630
Nobody cares about my life.

35
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:29,390
We can join hands.

36
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,630
Why?

37
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,190
To help you of course.

38
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,240
Help me what?

39
00:02:34,830 --> 00:02:35,800
To help you and the Empress Dowager

40
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,110
take over power from

41
00:02:37,110 --> 00:02:37,830
your little emperor.

42
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,000
Nonsense!

43
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:40,750
Who told you I'm with the Empress Dowager.

44
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,830
Your teacher Ku He is the Imperial Tutor.

45
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,080
She certainly has to take side.

46
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,160
As to the political fights of Beiqi,

47
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,390
there are mainly three forces.

48
00:02:53,110 --> 00:02:54,160
One is led by the little emperor.

49
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,910
One is led by the Empress Dowager.

50
00:02:56,270 --> 00:02:57,600
And the other is led by Shangshan Hu,

51
00:02:57,720 --> 00:02:58,630
which remains neutral.

52
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:01,080
Shangshan Hu wants to save Xiao En,

53
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:01,960
while you want to kill him.

54
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:03,550
You're certainly not on the same side.

55
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,360
I could also be a follower of His Majesty.

56
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,080
The little emperor made it clear that

57
00:03:08,110 --> 00:03:09,270
he wants Si Lili back.

58
00:03:09,550 --> 00:03:11,360
If you kill Xiao En in Nanqing,

59
00:03:11,390 --> 00:03:12,830
the mission will have to go back.

60
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,630
Then Si Lili won't be sent to Beiqi.

61
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,800
So you can't be a follower of

62
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,830
the little emperor.

63
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:20,470
In this case,

64
00:03:21,630 --> 00:03:23,160
you can only be with the Empress Dowager.

65
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,520
Even if you guessed right,

66
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,630
how can you help me?

67
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:34,830
I'm the envoy of Nanqing after all.

68
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,080
The two of us joining hands together

69
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:38,110
is beyond all expectations.

70
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,470
By doing so, we'll have everything to gain

71
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,440
and nothing to lose.

72
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,600
You actually know you're from Nanqing.

73
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,880
Yet you want to interfere with political affairs of Beiqi.

74
00:03:51,550 --> 00:03:52,440
I just have a feeling that

75
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:54,240
it'll be extremely difficult

76
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:56,360
for me to bring Yan Bingyun back.

77
00:03:57,910 --> 00:03:59,520
We're kind of helping each other out.

78
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:04,910
You've eaten my fruit after all.

79
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,830
Last night the rain was light, the wind was fierce,

80
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,830
and deep sleep did not dispel the effects of wine.

81
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,550
When I ask the maid rolling up the curtains,

82
00:04:17,790 --> 00:04:19,230
she answers, "The crabapple blossoms look the same."

83
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,390
I cry, "Can't you see? Can't you see?

84
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,200
The green leaves are fresh but the red flowers are fading!"
('crabapple' has the same meaning as 'Haitang' in Chinese)

85
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,070
It's for you.

86
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:29,760
It's kind of celebrating our cooperation.

87
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:32,510
Poetic Genius Fan.

88
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:33,320
What do you think?

89
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,110
The crabapple blossoms can't be exposed to the rain.

90
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:37,160
Caught in wind and rain, the pot will gather water.

91
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,760
The crabapple blossoms will rot

92
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,200
instead of fading.

93
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,390
I'll take that as a "Yes".

94
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:51,440
Shen Zhong, Commander-in-chief of Embroidered Uniform Guards,

95
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,270
will receive the mission in person.

96
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,720
Watch out yourself!

97
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,070
What's his character?

98
00:04:56,550 --> 00:04:57,640
Does he have any weakness?

99
00:04:58,390 --> 00:04:59,270
Before reaching Shangjing,

100
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,110
I won't give up on killing Xiao En.

101
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:13,600
Let's go.

102
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:15,270
Your Excellency, congratulations!

103
00:05:17,550 --> 00:05:18,270
For what?

104
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:21,670
Do you have a thing for the Saintess?

105
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:30,440
Your Excellency, don't worry.

106
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,200
We won't tell Princess Lin

107
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,000
about this.

108
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,480
Gao, how come you're also

109
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,230
making fun of me?

110
00:05:35,670 --> 00:05:37,830
Thanks for Wang's detailed explanation,

111
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,270
I've known Your Excellency well.

112
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,880
Your Excellency! Your Excellency! Your Excellency!

113
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:48,550
Your Excellency!

114
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,830
How are your wounds?

115
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,670
Do you feel better?

116
00:05:57,350 --> 00:05:58,480
You and Duoduo...

117
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:01,160
Don't listen to Wang Qinian.

118
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,200
That is not an aphrodisiac.

119
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,070
I've explained to her clearly.

120
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:07,160
Your Excellency,

121
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:09,480
after arriving in Beiqi,

122
00:06:09,670 --> 00:06:10,790
I won't go back to Nanqing ever again.

123
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,550
If you tell me,

124
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,160
I won't tell your wife.

125
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,670
Now I can't clear my name

126
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:17,920
even if I jump into the Yellow River.

127
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,640
Which river is that?

128
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,760
I just made it up.

129
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,070
Do you know Haitang Duoduo?

130
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,790
Yes.

131
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:28,920
We once had tea together in Shangjing Town.

132
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,200
Is that the capital of Beiqi?

133
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,440
Yes.

134
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,230
She doesn't look like a Saintess.

135
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:39,720
I envy her character all the time.

136
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:43,200
She's free, easy, pure, and lovely.

137
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:45,640
You're perfect for each other.

138
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,920
Let me ask you something.

139
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:55,640
Something private about Duoduo?

140
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,720
No!

141
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,350
I want to ask

142
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,000
why you took the arrow for me.

143
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:07,790
I...

144
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:11,830
I didn't intend to.

145
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:14,320
Seeing the arrow coming from the corner of my eye,

146
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,160
I just went to you.

147
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,350
I had no time to think.

148
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:25,110
To be honest,

149
00:07:26,790 --> 00:07:28,040
I still regret it now.

150
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,550
Your Excellency, no need to bother.

151
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:34,040
After sending me back to Beiqi,

152
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,790
we're even.

153
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,070
We'll reach Beiqi soon.

154
00:07:48,110 --> 00:07:49,390
You're poisoned.

155
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:51,070
According to the Red Sleeve Edict Scheme,

156
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:52,270
your little emperor of Beiqi is supposed to

157
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,920
be killed by the poison on your body.

158
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,600
Why do you tell me?

159
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,320
This is the antidote.

160
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,110
Only after you're detoxified

161
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:06,670
can we really be even.

162
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,390
What about you?

163
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,000
Who would know I'm the one

164
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,790
to detoxify you?

165
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,350
The poison could be ineffective

166
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:20,390
due to a wrong formula.

167
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,550
If I give this away,

168
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:32,110
you'll be in trouble, right?

169
00:08:36,110 --> 00:08:36,910
Will you?

170
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:40,590
Who knows what will happen in future?

171
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:42,790
Then let's wait and see.

172
00:09:47,470 --> 00:09:48,790
Your Excellency, your hair style is good.

173
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,080
Your clothes are so bright and shining.

174
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:52,200
Well, leave us alone.

175
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,710
Senior.

176
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,840
We've arrived in Beiqi.

177
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,400
It's your last chance

178
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,840
to kill me.

179
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,150
What's your hidden secret?

180
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:11,520
This is also your last chance to question me.

181
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:15,910
Why did you ask me

182
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,030
about Danzhou?

183
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,080
What's your relation with Danzhou?

184
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,640
Fine.

185
00:10:30,350 --> 00:10:31,400
Senior Xiao,

186
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:33,470
let's make a bet.

187
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:35,670
This won't be my last question

188
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:36,760
for you.

189
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,000
You're home.

190
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,200
Now that we're in Beiqi,

191
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:12,520
I won't be able to visit you often.

192
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:14,590
Take care of yourself.

193
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:20,520
Your Excellency, thank you for looking after me all the way.

194
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,470
Who is to receive us?

195
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:39,440
Your Excellency, it's weird.

196
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:41,150
There are people receiving us,

197
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,840
but no one answers back.

198
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,150
I'll say it one more time.

199
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:53,230
The Nanqing mission is here to return prisoners of war.

200
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,520
Who's in charge?

201
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,440
Please answer back at once.

202
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:07,880
If you remain silent, we'll leave right away.

203
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:33,150
Your Excellency, they're here.

204
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,400
What are you waiting for?

205
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:38,200
Your Excellency!

206
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:48,320
=Shen Zhong, Commander-in-chief of Embroidered Uniform Guards=

207
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:48,980
Are they here?
=Shen Zhong, Commander-in-chief of Embroidered Uniform Guards=

208
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:49,030
Are they here?

209
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:10,880
Excuse me, which one is His Excellency Fan Xian,

210
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:12,470
the Poetic Genius from Nanqing?

211
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:16,960
This is His Excellency Fan Xian,

212
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,640
Envoy of Nanqing.

213
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:21,470
Poetic Genius Fan!

214
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:22,590
I'm Fan Xian.

215
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,960
I've looked up to your great name for a long time!

216
00:13:25,230 --> 00:13:26,080
On seeing you today,

217
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,910
you're really outstanding as expected.

218
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:29,000
You are?

219
00:13:29,470 --> 00:13:30,520
I'm Shen Zhong.

220
00:13:30,590 --> 00:13:32,030
Just call me by my name.

221
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,280
Your Excellency Shen,
Commander-in-chief of Embroidered Uniform Guards.

222
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:35,960
You two should deal with

223
00:13:36,230 --> 00:13:37,150
the handover procedures.

224
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,400
Yes, Your Excellency.

225
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:41,110
Your Excellency Fan, have you heard of me?

226
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:42,080
Yes.

227
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,030
Your Excellency Shen, why not wear your robe?

228
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,550
My robe doesn't fit.

229
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,880
It's being altered in Shangjing.

230
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:50,280
Your Excellency Fan, I beg you pardon.

231
00:13:50,350 --> 00:13:51,200
That's fine! That's fine!

232
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,230
Where's Miss Si?

233
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:55,030
This way, please.

234
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,400
Your Excellency Shen, won't you check her out?

235
00:14:01,670 --> 00:14:03,880
It's fine. The mammies will handle it.

236
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,640
By the imperial edict of His Majesty,

237
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:07,520
Miss Si, we're here to escort you to Shangjing.

238
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:08,960
Please come with us.

239
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:10,640
I'm a new official.

240
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,350
In a high position at such a young age,

241
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,910
you do have a successful official career.

242
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:16,790
I'm just lucky.

243
00:14:17,030 --> 00:14:18,230
Your Excellency Shen, I'm really flattered.

244
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,910
You're the one

245
00:14:19,910 --> 00:14:21,000
who's really in a high position.

246
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,710
Miss Si, you're injured?

247
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:24,400
Hold her.

248
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,960
Miss Si is injured!

249
00:14:31,110 --> 00:14:31,840
Mammy,

250
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,150
on our way here,

251
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:34,230
some bandits pretended to be

252
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,400
the followers of Shangshan Hu,

253
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,470
trying to take Xiao En away.

254
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:38,670
Miss Si was shot accidentally.

255
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,640
She's fine now.

256
00:14:39,710 --> 00:14:41,790
How can you let her be injured?

257
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:43,710
Do you want to lose your head?

258
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:46,230
Who is she?

259
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,880
She's an old servant in the imperial palace.

260
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,320
Your Excellency Shen, no need to be flattering.

261
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,200
Unlike Nanqing,

262
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:56,470
Beiqi is a great country.

263
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,000
Such a great country was actually

264
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,670
so defeated as to cede territory for mercy.

265
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,200
What did you just say?

266
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,590
I said Beiqi lost the war

267
00:15:04,590 --> 00:15:05,550
and was utterly humiliated.

268
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:06,590
How dare you!

269
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,350
Let go of me!

270
00:15:08,350 --> 00:15:08,960
Mammy!

271
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,350
Let go!

272
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:12,080
-Let go! -Fine.

273
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,550
We Nanqing people are straight-forward.

274
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,670
You asked me to let go, so I let go.

275
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,080
Come on! Get up!

276
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,000
Look at you!

277
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:26,550
How could you watch him violate me

278
00:15:26,590 --> 00:15:29,350
on our territory?

