563
00:31:27,190 --> 00:31:28,190
Just like I said,

564
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,230
man should understand the situation.

565
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:31,800
Your Excellency Fan,

566
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:32,880
don't make it hard for me.

567
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:35,560
Take your time and enjoy the food.

568
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,430
Take them away.

569
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:08,470
He serves the Empress Dowager.

570
00:32:09,040 --> 00:32:10,160
So do you.

571
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:12,310
How come you two

572
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:13,350
are fighting each other?

573
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:18,160
My teacher wants to kill Xiao En.

574
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:20,280
As an apprentice, I have to obey her order.

575
00:32:25,110 --> 00:32:27,400
So I kind of saved your life.

576
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:29,830
You lifted the curtain just now.

577
00:32:30,070 --> 00:32:32,070
I'm bluffing. Don't you understand?

578
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:33,950
What if your plan doesn't work

579
00:32:33,950 --> 00:32:35,000
and he actually catches me?

580
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:36,230
Then so be it.

581
00:32:36,230 --> 00:32:37,310
How is that relevant to me?

582
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,070
Is it a joke for you?

583
00:32:41,470 --> 00:32:42,520
Will you assassinate Xiao En again?

584
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:45,830
I have no chance.

585
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,070
After entering Shangjing, I have no way to kill him.

586
00:32:48,430 --> 00:32:49,470
Then when we reach Shangjing,

587
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:50,280
let's cooperate with each other.

588
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:51,830
How?

589
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:52,800
Anyway you like.

590
00:32:53,310 --> 00:32:54,280
Whoever you find annoying,

591
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:55,310
I'll help you deal with him.

592
00:32:55,830 --> 00:32:57,280
By collaborating with me from within,

593
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:58,400
we can bring trouble to the country.

594
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,160
What's in it for you?

595
00:33:00,310 --> 00:33:01,280
I'm from Nanqing.

596
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,040
The more chaotic Beiqi is,

597
00:33:03,040 --> 00:33:04,040
the happier I will be.

598
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:05,880
I'm leaving.

599
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:07,560
Just think about it.

600
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,560
She's gone?

601
00:33:20,950 --> 00:33:21,800
Really?

602
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:26,800
She's gone.

603
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:30,880
It seems that Beiqi is really chaotic.

604
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:33,000
This might be our chance.

605
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:34,070
Right,

606
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:36,920
we can seize the chance to take the Saintess back.

607
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:38,520
What're you thinking?

608
00:33:39,070 --> 00:33:41,110
It's our chance to fulfill the mission task.

609
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,280
Right! Right! Right!

610
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:45,560
It's a good excuse to fool the public.

611
00:33:47,560 --> 00:33:48,230
Right!

612
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:49,760
Lend me some money.

613
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,520
Give me silver instead of bank notes.

614
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:59,160
I'll pay you twice as much when we go back to the capital city.

615
00:34:00,190 --> 00:34:01,000
Twice?

616
00:34:03,470 --> 00:34:05,110
You two, turn around.

617
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:23,560
What's up?

618
00:34:23,710 --> 00:34:24,670
At dawn tomorrow,

619
00:34:24,910 --> 00:34:25,840
you should leave on your own.

620
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,390
Don't let others see you.

621
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:28,910
Go south to Shangjing Town,

622
00:34:28,910 --> 00:34:30,320
and find a Tiaowang Inn.

623
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:32,320
Take the money, get yourself a room,

624
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,230
and stay there.

625
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,520
Why should I listen to you?

626
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:38,470
Only by helping me complete the task of the Investigator's Office

627
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,760
can you get your father out of the jail.

628
00:35:33,950 --> 00:35:35,470
Your Excellency, as you commanded,

629
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:36,950
our agents watch the place closely

630
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:38,150
and see a man from the Nanqing mission

631
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,390
slip away secretly.

632
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:41,280
Now he stays in an inn south of Shangjing.

633
00:35:41,670 --> 00:35:42,470
Should we catch him?

634
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,670
Leave him alone.

635
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:45,600
Let him stay there

636
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:46,870
as if we don't know.

637
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:48,470
Let's see what His Excellency Fan

638
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:50,320
will do next.

639
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,520
Yes.

640
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:02,120
Your Excellency, we've arrived in Shangjing Town.

641
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,190
After taking Yan Bingyun back,

642
00:36:04,430 --> 00:36:05,520
we can go home.

643
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:07,430
I'm afraid it's not that simple.

644
00:36:07,870 --> 00:36:09,280
Your Excellency, you feel something might go wrong.

645
00:36:15,390 --> 00:36:16,000
Look.

646
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,080
Here comes trouble.

647
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,470
Grand General!

648
00:36:27,630 --> 00:36:28,950
Whatever it is,

649
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:30,190
just send me a message.

650
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,600
How come you're here in person?

651
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:33,360
I want to see him?

652
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:35,560
See whom?

653
00:36:35,870 --> 00:36:36,800
My adoptive father.

654
00:36:37,430 --> 00:36:39,120
Who's your adoptive father?

655
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,360
Xiao En.

656
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:45,000
So Senior Xiao

657
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,560
is actually your adoptive father.

658
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,630
It's true that man from a military family

659
00:36:48,630 --> 00:36:49,600
is bound to be extraordinary.

660
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:51,000
Where is he?

661
00:36:51,230 --> 00:36:52,280
He's here! He's here!

662
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,470
Why is he so tortured?

663
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:18,080
I interrogated him according to the imperial edict.

664
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:19,760
You did this to him?

665
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:21,390
Yes.

666
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,840
Grand General, since he's your father,

667
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:29,120
you can have a closer look at him.

668
00:37:29,910 --> 00:37:30,710
It's a pity that

669
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:33,120
I broke his legs,

670
00:37:33,520 --> 00:37:34,760
or you might see him

671
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,360
stand up.

672
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,800
Grand General, are you satisfied with what you see?

673
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:46,670
Give him to me.

674
00:37:46,870 --> 00:37:47,710
I'm afraid I can't.

675
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:49,560
How dare you defy my order?

676
00:37:51,150 --> 00:37:52,560
Grand General, you don't know.

677
00:37:53,390 --> 00:37:55,560
His Majesty and the Empress Dowager of Beiqi

678
00:37:55,870 --> 00:37:57,040
ordered me to lock Xiao En up

679
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,040
in the Division of Embroidered Uniform Guards.

680
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,670
I can't defy the imperial order.

681
00:38:02,710 --> 00:38:04,800
Grand General, what else can I do for you?

682
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:16,360
Shen Zhong,

683
00:38:20,910 --> 00:38:22,190
good for you.

684
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:33,040
Grand General, thank you for the compliment.

685
00:38:33,950 --> 00:38:36,230
I'm just loyal to my country.

686
00:38:41,520 --> 00:38:42,280
Your Excellency,

687
00:38:42,710 --> 00:38:45,280
Shen Zhong is not good at dealing with other officials.

688
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,470
Right.

689
00:38:48,670 --> 00:38:50,800
He's vicious and cruel,

690
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:52,520
but he's too arrogant

691
00:38:52,670 --> 00:38:53,910
to restrain himself.

692
00:38:54,120 --> 00:38:55,520
It will definitely get him into trouble.

693
00:38:56,190 --> 00:38:56,910
Exactly.

694
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,280
Shangshan Hu almost

695
00:38:58,600 --> 00:39:00,040
attacked him just now.

696
00:39:00,710 --> 00:39:01,630
He did it on purpose.

697
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:03,870
On purpose?

698
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:06,280
From breaking Xiao En's legs on the border

699
00:39:06,800 --> 00:39:08,600
to torturing Xiao En cruelly along the way,

700
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:10,560
he did all that to provoke Shangshan Hu.

701
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,280
Make Shangshan Hu attack him?

702
00:39:13,390 --> 00:39:15,760
After all, Shangshan Hu has brilliant achievements in war.

703
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,760
To punish him,

704
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:18,430
there should be a reason.

705
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,870
By making him attack the mission,

706
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,950
Shangshan Hu can be accused of defying the imperial edict.

707
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,230
I'm afraid he will also

708
00:39:26,230 --> 00:39:27,230
be accused of treason.

709
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:30,670
Who gave the order,

710
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:31,950
the Empress Dowager of Beiqi or the little emperor?

711
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,280
Maybe both.

712
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,600
I didn't expect Shangshan Hu

713
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:40,320
to be so feared in Beiqi.

714
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:41,760
It's a good thing.

715
00:39:42,710 --> 00:39:43,600
Really?

716
00:39:45,670 --> 00:39:46,430
Your Excellency Fan,

717
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,560
His Majesty is anxious to see you.

718
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:49,630
I'm sorry that

719
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:50,630
you'll have to first meet His Majesty in the imperial palace

720
00:39:50,800 --> 00:39:51,870
and then go to your residence.

721
00:39:52,600 --> 00:39:53,520
We can go inside now.

722
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:15,120
Won't Miss Si Lili go to the imperial palace?

723
00:40:15,390 --> 00:40:16,280
She has no status.

724
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:18,080
She should live outside the imperial palace
and wait for the chance.

725
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:20,840
Are you familiar with Miss Lili?

726
00:40:21,910 --> 00:40:22,710
I caught her.

727
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:26,870
Won't Xiao En's carriage go inside the town?

728
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:28,870
He will go inside from the West Gate.

729
00:40:29,470 --> 00:40:30,670
You also see what happened just now.

730
00:40:31,190 --> 00:40:32,430
We don't know what will happen

731
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:33,560
when we go inside.

732
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:40,190
When two counties are at war, no messengers shall be killed.

733
00:40:40,910 --> 00:40:42,520
Nanqing has won a landslide victory this time.

734
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,910
When entering the town,

735
00:40:44,910 --> 00:40:46,430
we certainly won't see people
welcoming us on both sides of the street,

736
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:50,390
but they can't go so far as to throw rotten eggs at us.

737
00:40:53,230 --> 00:40:54,870
Get out of Beiqi!

738
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:56,950
No envoy from Nanqing is welcome!

739
00:40:57,040 --> 00:40:59,190
You! Get off!

740
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:00,600
Nanqing dogs!

741
00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:04,280
You're not welcome! You're not welcome!

742
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:06,560
Get out of Beiqi! Get off!

743
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:07,760
Throw at him!

744
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:10,760
Get off! Get off!

745
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:14,280
Get off! Get off!

746
00:41:15,430 --> 00:41:17,040
You're not welcome in Beiqi!

747
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:17,910
There're vegetables and eggs

748
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,320
enough for several meals.

749
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,190
Let's add dishes tonight.

750
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:21,560
Yes, Your Excellency.

751
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:23,320
Get off!

752
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:25,390
Get off, Nanqing dogs!

753
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,560
You're not welcome!

754
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:27,430
Get out of Beiqi.

755
00:41:27,950 --> 00:41:29,520
Our people are concerned about national affairs.

756
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:30,950
Since we lost the battle,

757
00:41:30,950 --> 00:41:32,280
they can't help feeling angry.

758
00:41:32,470 --> 00:41:33,760
I'm afraid they're not all common people.

759
00:41:34,390 --> 00:41:36,230
You killed Cheng Jushu,

760
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:38,430
the martial arts master of Beiqi, on the street.

761
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,670
Men in the army and on the streets who practice martial arts

762
00:41:40,870 --> 00:41:42,600
want to learn from you.

763
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,840
They are not bound by rules.

764
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:47,560
They might assassinate you or make a sneak attack.

765
00:41:48,390 --> 00:41:50,150
You'd better hide in the carriage.

766
00:41:50,870 --> 00:41:52,230
It won't take long.

767
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:54,710
The Embroidered Uniform Guards

768
00:41:54,710 --> 00:41:55,560
can't even keep their own capital under control?

769
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:57,840
I'm really not competent enough.

770
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:59,320
Sorry! Sorry!

771
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:01,430
As the envoy of Nanqing,

772
00:42:01,910 --> 00:42:03,710
if I hide in the carriage

773
00:42:03,950 --> 00:42:04,840
on my way to the imperial palace,

774
00:42:05,120 --> 00:42:06,120
I'm afraid I'll dishonor

775
00:42:06,150 --> 00:42:07,230
my country completely.

776
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,390
If you don't hide,

777
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:11,150
with more rotten vegetables and worn-out shoes coming,

778
00:42:11,230 --> 00:42:12,950
it's not so honorable, either.

779
00:42:13,430 --> 00:42:14,760
So I'll dishonor

780
00:42:14,760 --> 00:42:15,840
my country either way.

781
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:19,040
I just can't quell the public anger.

782
00:42:19,910 --> 00:42:21,320
You're really good.

783
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:22,760
You misunderstood me.

784
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:25,630
Wait!

785
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:27,710
Gao.

786
00:42:31,560 --> 00:42:32,910
There's a long roll of cloth on the carriage

787
00:42:32,910 --> 00:42:34,040
behind which carries cargos.

788
00:42:34,120 --> 00:42:34,950
Bring it to me.

789
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:36,040
Yes, Your Excellency.

790
00:43:04,540 --> 00:43:07,860
In the river of history,

791
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:11,060
time goes round and round.

792
00:43:14,420 --> 00:43:17,420
Memories about the former and present lives

793
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:21,300
join each other in an endless way.

794
00:43:23,740 --> 00:43:25,900
In the long drunken Milky Way,

795
00:43:26,380 --> 00:43:28,620
one season follows another in a flash,

796
00:43:28,620 --> 00:43:30,820
and the wild geese are flying south.

797
00:43:31,140 --> 00:43:32,740
I just can't give up

798
00:43:32,740 --> 00:43:35,740
to be with you for my whole life.

799
00:43:36,100 --> 00:43:41,020
I have been hovering in the dreams
for hundreds and thousands of times.

800
00:43:42,820 --> 00:43:44,820
I can't even say a word when I watch the flowers falling.

801
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:47,700
Year after year in the wandering,

802
00:43:47,700 --> 00:43:50,260
I count the remaining years.

803
00:43:50,380 --> 00:43:52,460
Even though we can't meet each other anymore,

804
00:43:52,580 --> 00:43:54,020
even though we have ended up the destiny,

805
00:43:54,860 --> 00:43:56,700
I never feel regretful.

806
00:43:57,300 --> 00:43:58,660
In such a chaotic world,

807
00:43:58,660 --> 00:44:01,420
I still miss you as ever.

808
00:44:01,660 --> 00:44:04,060
I can't fall asleep under the moon.

809
00:44:04,900 --> 00:44:06,780
With a gentle heart,

810
00:44:06,980 --> 00:44:09,340
I cherish our remaining years.

811
00:44:09,660 --> 00:44:11,180
Even though we have to go through

812
00:44:11,180 --> 00:44:13,140
all the hardships along the journey,

813
00:44:13,820 --> 00:44:20,460
you always stay by my side,

814
00:44:21,100 --> 00:44:23,220
watching the falling flowers, speechlessly.

